original: Ehrnst, Olle, tandläkare, Töreboda, f. 9/1/06 i Reppiinge, Kalm. 1., av dir. John E. o. Anna von Mentzer. G. 34 m. Anna Lisa Beskow. Barn: Ann-Sofie f. 36, Odle 38, Gunnar 40. — Stud :ex. i Kristianst. 24, med. kand. v. Karoi. inst. 27, tandläk. 32. Vik. i Hälsingb. 32-33, i Trelleb. 33, förest, f. Sv. Röda Korsets ambuler. tand-klin. inom Jämtl. län samt praktik i Töreboda sed. 43.
translated: Ehrnst, Olle, dentist, Töreboda, b. 9/1/06 in Reppiinge, Kalm. County, son of director John E. and Anna von Mentzer. Married in 1934 to Anna Lisa Beskow. Children: Ann-Sofie b. 1936, Odle b. 1938, Gunnar b. 1940. Education: student exam in Kristianst. in 1924, medical candidate at Karolinska Institute in 1927, dentist degree in 1932. Worked in Hälsingborg temporary in 1932-1933, in Trelleborg in 1933, and managed the Swedish Red Cross' mobile dental clinic in Jämtland County as well as dental practice in Töreboda since 1943.
